{"tid":2114700,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"乒球群組五個案 真光女帶病考試","createTime":"2020-07-19T04:42:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-19T05:40:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"96143071b7add612bfcb1a03455b783a73338644","tid":2114700,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:42:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200719/KQQDU6YFQQVLCVD7OPB4KK7WLA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200719%2FKQQDU6YFQQVLCVD7OPB4KK7WLA%2F&d=Se3jk6qONbDe%2BTgec%2FNeB26H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=528c79ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200719%2FKQQDU6YFQQVLCVD7OPB4KK7WLA%2F&h=997d1826\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200719/KQQDU6YFQQVLCVD7OPB4KK7WLA/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n乒球群組五個案 真光女帶病考試<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/OxU5ZYT7FN-hqncNw_FNI4CWwe4=/425x304/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/I7MAR5DKDNRMKUYJDNV2ZJ2A2I.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOxU5ZYT7FN-hqncNw_FNI4CWwe4%3D%2F425x304%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FI7MAR5DKDNRMKUYJDNV2ZJ2A2I.gif&h=be21e966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n新蒲崗捷菁乒乓球體育中心早前聘消毒公司為場所消毒。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】昨新增多個確診群組，其中「乒乓球群組」涉及五人，他們早前曾一同到新蒲崗捷菁乒乓球體育中心。中心負責人表示，當日有不多於25人包場。油麻地真光女書院亦有學生確診，她曾在發病後回校考試。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：「港版火神山」擬接收輕症患者<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n疑聊天飲食受感染<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君昨指，。。。。。。。。。。。。。離較遠，料感染風險不大。<br />\n<br />\n新蒲崗捷菁乒乓球體育中心負責人陳先生昨晚指，「乒乓球群組」本月9日曾到球會進行例行包場練習，。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n陳先生指，球會內乒乓球桌。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另外，個案1733號16歲女子就讀油麻地真光女書院。她7月11日開始咳嗽，但仍於7月12日及13日回校考試。張竹君指會追蹤緊密接觸者，並會派發深喉唾液樣本樽予同學及老師。"},{"pid":"b14fe5d83ef45d3fe85ed8a0e14f9b00b6e73938","tid":2114700,"uid":185492,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:57:09.000Z","msg":"個波有毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c4f32000707bcc2597ac1a6e628f3f7d719b6dc","tid":2114700,"uid":49359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:57:32.000Z","msg":"係唔係教育局講左提前放暑假之後考？<br />\n我見話放暑假後<br />\n仲見真光妹返學<br />\n當時我心諗成績真係大過條命"},{"pid":"dd6339dd5258a0d878cd84b1583aea7778cfc645","tid":2114700,"uid":99828,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T05:00:21.000Z","msg":"考運局話考試低風險吖嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔會咁易傳人吖嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211f76f97c83f94c6cdaa0fc607f684523b218cf","tid":2114700,"uid":20563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4c4f32000707bcc2597ac1a6e628f3f7d719b6dc","tid":2114700,"uid":49359,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T04:57:32.000Z","msg":"係唔係教育局講左提前放暑假之後考？<br />\n我見話放暑假後<br />\n仲見真光妹返學<br />\n當時我心諗成績真係大過條命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T05:02:55.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】教育局繼宣布提早放暑假後，進一步收緊學校防疫措施，明日起除考試外，暫停校內活動兩周，學生如非必要不應回校。<br />\n<br />\n教育局向全港學校發通告，指鑑於疫情繼續有擴散迹象，教育局經通盤考慮後，決定學校由周三起，暫停所有校內活動兩星期，包括所有級別補課及課外活動，直至本月28日，其間如非必要學生不應回校。<br />\n<br />\n另外，教育局早前容許學校本周內完成重要級別考試，局方要求學校盡快在兩、三天內完成所有考試，或延後、取消部分考試，以便盡早開始放暑假。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=397881\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D397881&d=Se3jk6qONbDe%2BTgec%2FNeB26H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=3dc72f85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D397881&h=c7576374\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=397881</a><br />\n<br />\n的確係班友大大聲俾學校考試。你放寬俾人考試，d 人仲唔狗衝去考咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" 